Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:59.62,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Chystáš sa tiež vstúpiť do súťaže krásy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:41.05,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobré ráno, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:46.97,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Už si sa zobudil?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:55.40,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Ty si ale spachtoš, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:07.13,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, mali by sme sa poponáhľať,\N lebo budeme meškať.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.17,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudla si niečo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:17.79,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Som v pohode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:18.92,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Tak, môžeme ísť.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:38.69,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to už doba, čo sme išli spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.64,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Mali by sme už ísť domov, Nii-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:33.08,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:35.69,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hlúpy, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.70,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… to bolo dobré.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:51.74,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem ti za jedlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:54.76,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo si myslíš o mojich vlastnostiach?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.14,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Vlastnosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:56.87,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Moje?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.43,0:20:58.31,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje vlastnosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.35,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Nemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:06.61,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš čaj?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.15,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:36.19,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.15,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hlúpy, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:50.75,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten Nii-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:56.12,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Otvoril dvere do kúpeľne...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:57.74,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,... mal by byť viac opatrný.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.00,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Musím ísť spať.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.92,0:22:12.18,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobrú noc.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:15.05,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej, Nemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.05,0:22:16.55,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Choď spať do svojej izby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.22,0:22:18.14,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Hej!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.91,0:22:21.94,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nedá sa ti pomôcť.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.72,0:23:18.83,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:19.65,tit,,0000,0000,0000,,Nepozeraj sa!
